<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَكُلُّ شَرَابٍ مُسْكِرٍ:</span> يَحْرُمُ مُطْلَقاً.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- إِلَّا لِدَفْعِ لُقْمَةٍ غُصَّ بِهَا <span class="c2">(١)</span>، مَعَ خَوْفِ تَلَفٍ، وَيُقَدَّمُ عَلَيْهِ بَوْلٌ. ظظ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- فَإِذَا شَرِبَهُ، أَوِ احْتَقَنَ بِهِ مُسْلِمٌ، مُكَلَّفٌ، مُخْتَاراً،<span class="c5"> عَالِماً أَنَّ كَثِيرَهُ يُسْكِرُ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> حُدَّ حُرٌّ:</span> ثَمَانِينَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَقِنٌّ:</span> نِصْفَهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَثْبُتُ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> بِإِقْرَارِهِ مَرَّةً؛ كَقَذْفٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> أَوْ شَهَادَةِ عَدْلَيْنِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَحَرُمَ عَصِيرٌ وَنَحْوُهُ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- إِذَا غَلَى.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- أَوْ أَتَى عَلَيْهِ ثَلَاثَةُ أَيَّامٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قوله: (بها) سقطت من (د).</p> </div>